        "We can also use the function scipy's `quad` functionnfor defining the Fourier transform of a function `f` at a given frequency `nu`.  The function `tf_integral` below implements this approach. It uses numerical integration to compute the Fourier transform of a function `f` over the interval $[-T/2, T/2]$.\n"
      ],
